creator: Cuballama
descriptionHtml:
Cuballama, the easiest way to recharge phones worldwide.

Calls to Cuba and the world at the best price.

You have family or friends who live in another country? Use the application Cuballama send money to their cell, from the convenience of your mobile.

You can also send text messages (SMS) to everyone.

Follow us on:
https://www.facebook.com/CubaLlama
https://twitter.com/CubaLlama
descriptionShort: Cuballama, the easiest way to recharge phones worldwide.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Hemos desarrollado un nuevo app desde cero, pensando en ti.
-Ahora el login y registro sólo requiere la entrada de tu número de teléfono. No necesitas memorizar contraseña.
-Puedes programar tu Recarga celular a Cuba o hacerla en el instante.
-Las recargas Cubacel y Nauta llegan a tu familia ahora más rápido.
-Nuevo sistema de llamadas con aún mejor calidad, a través de wifi, datos móviles, y números de acceso locales.
-Nuevos métodos de pago: Google Pay y pago en efectivo para latinoamérica.

Hemos desarrollado un nuevo app desde cero, pensando en ti.
-Ahora el login y registro sólo requiere la entrada de tu número de teléfono. No necesitas memorizar contraseña.
-Puedes programar tu Recarga celular a Cuba o hacerla en el instante.
-Las recargas Cubacel y Nauta llegan a tu familia ahora más rápido.
-Nuevo sistema de llamadas con aún mejor calidad, a través de wifi, datos móviles, y números de acceso locales.
-Nuevos métodos de pago: Google Pay y pago en efectivo para latinoamérica.

title: Cuballama

creator: Cuballama
descriptionHtml:
Cuballama, the easiest way to recharge phones worldwide.

Calls to Cuba and the world at the best price.

You have family or friends who live in another country? Use the application Cuballama send money to their cell, from the convenience of your mobile.

You can also send text messages (SMS) to everyone.

Follow us on:
https://www.facebook.com/CubaLlama
https://twitter.com/CubaLlama

creator: Cuballama
descriptionHtml:
Discover the #1 services app for Cuba. The perfect tool to stay close to your loved ones and enjoy practical services designed with their needs in mind.

What can you do with Cuballama?
● Phone recharges: Send balance to Cuba and other countries in seconds, with frequent promotions to make the most of your money.
● Cuballama Mercado: Buy groceries, essential products, and more, delivered directly to your relatives’ homes in Cuba.
● Phone calls: Easily call Cuba and other countries with exceptional quality.
● Cuballama Viajes: Plan your dream vacation, send tickets to your relatives in Cuba and around the world, and rent a car in Cuba with those who know the terrain best.
● Cuballama Envíos: Have your gifts or purchases delivered reliably to your loved ones’ doorstep.
● Cuballama Balance: The easiest way to support family and friends by transferring the amount they need so they can make their own purchases.

Advantages of using Cuballama:
● Easy to use: An intuitive, user-friendly design that lets you take care of everything in just a few steps.
● Exclusive promotions: Enjoy unique offers on recharges, shipments, and more.
● Personalized support: Always by your side with fast, efficient customer service via the app, the web, Facebook, Instagram, phone, and at our stores in Miami, Houston, Las Vegas, Kentucky, and Madrid.
● Guaranteed security: Your transactions are protected with state-of-the-art technology.

Why choose Cuballama?
Because we know how important it is to be close to your loved ones, even when you’re far away. With Cuballama, you have the easiest, fastest, and most reliable way to support your family, connect with friends, and simplify your life.

Download the app today and start enjoying the benefits thousands of users already love.
Cuballama, one Cuban family!

Available for Android.

Follow us on:
Facebook >> https://www.facebook.com/FamiliaCuballama
Instagram >> https://www.instagram.com/cuballama_oficial/
descriptionShort: No. 1 app for services to Cuba
